{"word":"νομίζω","slug":"νομίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>νομίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νόμος\">νόμος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘practice what is customary’ (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νόμος\">νόμος</a></el>), <b>hold in common use,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὗ\">οὗ</a> ἐνομίζετο προσευχὴ εἶναι</el> where according to custom was a place of prayer <b><a href='B:510 16:13'>Ac 16:13</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘determine on the basis of ordinary reasoning’, <b>think, conclude, suppose, be of the opinion (that) <a href='B:470 5:17'>Mt 5:17</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:νομή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:νομικός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}